tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE PriceTimePriority (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    price DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    time TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    priority INT NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE OrderHistory (
    order_id INT,
    symbol VARCHAR(255),
    price DECIMAL(10,2),
    time TIMESTAMP,
    status VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE ExecutionHistory (
    execution_id INT,
    order_id INT,
    price DECIMAL(10,2),
    time TIMESTAMP,
    executed_volume INT
);

CREATE TABLE execution_details (
    trade_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    symbol TEXT,
    price FLOAT,
    quantity INT,
    time TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    symbol TEXT,
    price FLOAT,
    quantity INT,
    time TIMESTAMP,
    priority INT
);

CREATE TABLE trade_history (
    trade_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    symbol TEXT,
    price FLOAT,
    quantity INT,
    time TIMESTAMP,
    executed_price FLOAT,
    executed_quantity INT
);
